{"word":"G1256 - διαλέγομαι - dialégomai - dee-al-eg'-om-ahee - Dispute","slug":"G1256","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διαλέγομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>dialégomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>dee-al-eg'-om-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Dispute"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B4;&#x03B9;&#x03B1;&#x03BB;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03B3;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - dialegomai</b> - <i>dee-al-eg'-om-ahee</i><p/>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G3004\">G3004</a>; to <i>say thoroughly</i>, that is, <i>discuss</i> (in argument or exhortation): - dispute, preach (unto), reason (with), speak."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1260\">G1260</a>, <a href=\"#/G1261\">G1261</a>"}]}